@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@categoryId = REPLACE_WITH_A_CATEGORY_ID
@userId = REPLACE_WITH_A_BUYER_ID

### List categories (scoped per user via query) — GET /categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?createdByUserId={{userId}}

### Create a new category — POST /categories/create
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Home",
  "createdByUserId": "{{userId}}"
}

### Get a category by id — GET /categories/:id
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}

### Update a category by id — PATCH /categories/:id
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Household"
}

### Bulk-update categories matching a query — PATCH /categories
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories?createdByUserId={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Renamed"
}

### Delete a category by id (cascades: clears it from referencing duties) — DELETE /categories/:id
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}

### Bulk-delete categories matching a query — DELETE /categories
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories?createdByUserId={{userId}}
